\id 2TH - Uare 
\h 2Tesalonika 
\toc3 2Tes 
\toc2 2Tesalonika 
\toc1 Tesalonika Ekalesia veize Pauloꞌa Mirihiroteꞌe Soꞌaḡa Aheuḡa 
\mt1 2Tesalonika  
\mt2 Tesalonika Ekalesia veize Pauloꞌa Mirihiroteꞌe Soꞌaḡa Aheuḡa  
\imt1 Ihore Ḡoeꞌa  
\ip Soꞌa ꞌahiꞌe Pauloꞌa Korinto zamaḡano Tesalonika ekalesia veize mirihiro. Tesalonikaꞌe Makedonia habaꞌano ne boro ꞌahoga. Pauloꞌa ibite soꞌa ꞌahoga tuḡuriro ebu soꞌa ꞌahiꞌe aheuḡa. Tesalonika ekalesia azaḡaniꞌa Iesuꞌa bare ariteꞌe moneo veꞌone ederiro. Vaze nuꞌa Iesuꞌe amahi ariro rae ḡoeriro. Eꞌanoꞌo Pauloꞌa Iesuꞌe ꞌize mene ariroteꞌe zu aniꞌa bare ariteꞌe madaḡaꞌe Badiꞌa daꞌo edeḡa rae ihoziro. Ebu ekalesia azaḡaꞌe izidionoꞌo onamo Iesuꞌa bare ariteꞌe madaḡano fie gigaruꞌenaꞌa zu haḡai manoḡa haḡaeꞌenaꞌa zu zamaze obone giganeꞌenaꞌa, faine gaue radiꞌuma rae inaraziro.  
\c 1  
\p
\v 1 Eḡe, Paulo zu Silasi ebu Timoteoꞌa Badiꞌa emeḡe Mama zu Zuhiꞌa Boro Iesu Keriso mone azaḡa, Tesalonika ekalesia veize soꞌa ꞌahi miriheꞌohe.  
\v 2 Badiꞌa emeḡe Mama zu Zuhiꞌa Boro Iesu Kerisoꞌa manoḡa zu zama roḡeḡa ziniꞌenoꞌi.   
\s1 Badiꞌa mazao Manoḡa Tauḡi Raꞌohe  
\p
\v 3 Nego nabudi, eme zae uꞌano iḡaiḡa Badiꞌa mazao manoḡa tauḡi reꞌuma. Eme ꞌouge haḡaeꞌetaꞌaꞌe duduḡa. Mazaḡa zaꞌa fieꞌeteꞌeꞌa bororu onameꞌohe, ebu zae niduꞌa zamarotiteꞌetaꞌaꞌe zuni bororuꞌohe.  
\v 4 Eꞌanoꞌo habaꞌahabaꞌano Badiꞌa mone ekalesiaḡa nunu mazao za niguzeꞌohe. Mazaḡa zaꞌe vazeꞌa aduga ziniꞌeteꞌe zu agiroziꞌeteꞌe zamaḡano zuni zamaze obone giganeꞌohe ebu fie gigaruꞌohe.   
\s1 Kerisoꞌa Onaiteꞌe madaḡano Kotaziꞌuma  
\p
\v 5 ꞌAhiguḡa niduꞌa Badiꞌa kotaꞌe duduḡa rae ihozeꞌohe. Badiꞌaꞌa zaꞌe aniꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe azaḡano rouga veize ohoziro. Eꞌe uꞌano, zaeꞌa aduga zuni hideꞌohe.  
\v 6 Badiꞌaꞌe iniuꞌa vaze aduga ziniꞌeteꞌe azaḡa naenaeziꞌuma. Aniꞌa za aduga ziniꞌeteꞌe azaḡa aduga hina naenaeziꞌohe.  
\v 7 Ebu za, aduga hideꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa ahiri ohoneꞌeteꞌe madaḡa ziniꞌuma ebu emeḡe zuni rifiꞌuma. Aꞌe Zuhiꞌa Boro Iesuꞌa ane tuḡure viga inaraḡa ḡehaḡa teite adureonoꞌo ire roga duhuḡa zamaḡano ovaiteꞌe madaḡano fureraꞌuma.  
\v 8 Eꞌe madaḡano Iesuꞌa Badiꞌa aḡuꞌa azaḡa zu emeḡe Zuhiꞌa Boro Iesu hariḡa manoḡa mene egohauꞌeteꞌe azaḡa aduga ziniꞌuma.  
\v 9 Zeꞌe aduga hidadu rudaꞌuma, onamo tuḡutuḡu. Ebu zeꞌe Zuhiꞌa Boro mazaonoꞌo zu ane inaraḡa boro bagaḡaonoꞌo mae vaḡiziꞌuma.  
\v 10 Eꞌe madaḡano Zuhiꞌa Boroꞌa arine, ane mone azaḡaniꞌa ane ni mae ḡihiniꞌuma ebu fieꞌeteꞌe azaḡa niduꞌa ane niguniꞌuma. Mazaḡa zaꞌe emeꞌa rae fureniroteꞌe hariḡa mae ḡihiniro.   
\p
\v 11 Eꞌe uꞌano, emeꞌa zae veize iḡaiḡa kurauꞌohe. Aꞌe emeḡe Badiꞌaꞌa zae huzadu zaeꞌa ane urao radifine raꞌohe. Ebu aniꞌa inaraḡa zenadu zaeꞌa haḡai manoḡa niduꞌa haḡaihi rae raꞌeteꞌe zamaroneḡa meifine, zu zaeꞌa fieꞌenaꞌa haḡai niduꞌa haḡaifine kurauꞌohe.  
\v 12 ꞌOugine, emeḡe Badiꞌa zu Zuhiꞌa Boro Iesu Kerisoꞌa manoḡa furenozenadu zaeꞌa emeḡe Zuhiꞌa Boro Iesu niḡa mae ḡihiniꞌuma zu aniꞌa zae ni zuni mae ḡihiniꞌuma.   
\c 2  
\s1 Badiꞌa Goro Ḡoeꞌa Varadeꞌeteꞌe Vazeḡa  
\p
\v 1 Nego nabudi, emeḡe Zuhiꞌa Boro Iesu Kerisoꞌa bare ariteꞌe moneo zu emeḡe niduꞌa Iesu zamao nuꞌoratiteꞌe moneo emeꞌa ḡoreziꞌuma.  
\v 2 Vaze nuꞌa ꞌahige raꞌohe, “Zuhiꞌa Boroꞌa ariteꞌe madaḡa ꞌai amahi feuriro.” Ze zeḡeꞌa bare Badiꞌaꞌa ohozadu ꞌouge ziꞌohe rae raꞌohe, ga zeḡe haramo hina ꞌouge ziꞌohe. Zeꞌe emeḡe mazaonoꞌo meiroteꞌe soꞌaḡa idunaḡano ꞌouge ziꞌohe rae raꞌenaꞌa, zae soꞌozeꞌohe. Zaꞌe zeḡe ḡoere egadu zamaze ago ḡarihe hagaroꞌi zu ꞌadaꞌadazoꞌi.  
\v 3 Iniuꞌa ibi nunuo zae soꞌosoꞌozeꞌeteꞌe gararoꞌi. Mazaḡa Zuhiꞌa Boroꞌa ꞌizema arogano, vaze ḡehaḡaniꞌa Badiꞌa agirohaꞌuma ebu ḡonagano Badiꞌaꞌa ruiniteꞌe vazeḡa mazao sauꞌa huneḡaniꞌa fureraꞌuma. Aniꞌe Badiꞌa goro ḡoeꞌa varadeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa.  
\v 4 Aniꞌe badiꞌa rae huneꞌeteꞌe ḡauḡa niduꞌa zu vazeꞌa kuranohauꞌeteꞌe ḡauḡa niduꞌa agiroziꞌuma ebu eꞌe niduꞌa rana ane ni mae ḡihiniꞌuma. Ebu aniꞌe Badiꞌa kuru neḡano ehoradu aneꞌa bare, “Eꞌe Badiꞌa,” rae fureniꞌuma.   
\p
\v 5 Eꞌeguḡa moneo e zae teite radiunuteꞌe madaḡano ziro. Za mene zamareꞌehe?  
\v 6 Ebu za edeḡa, izidi ḡau ꞌahoganiꞌa vaze sauꞌa huneḡa eꞌe ꞌueꞌohe, rehano ane madaꞌa arine aniꞌa fureraꞌuma.  
\v 7 Badiꞌa goro ḡoeꞌa varadeꞌeteꞌe zamaroneḡaniꞌa sifu inare gaueꞌohe, rehano hunioꞌe mene fureraꞌuma. Mazaḡa vaze sauꞌa huneḡaniꞌa gauiteꞌe ibiḡaꞌe vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa ꞌuiꞌuma, onamo vaze sauꞌa huneḡa eꞌe ꞌueꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaniꞌa vaḡiniꞌuma.  
\v 8 Ebu hena Badiꞌa goro ḡoeꞌa varadeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa eꞌeꞌa fureraꞌuma. Eꞌe madaḡano Zuhiꞌa Boro Iesuꞌa hebeꞌanonoꞌo irineḡa hina maꞌuma, ebu Iesuꞌa arine agaḡa boro hina ruiniꞌuma.  
\v 9 Badiꞌa goro ḡoeꞌa varadeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa eꞌeꞌa Satani inaraḡa madu ariꞌuma ebu Satani gauḡa haḡaiꞌuma. Aniꞌa aradu haḡai gigiꞌa nunu, haḡai nu badeḡa, zu zaguzagatiteꞌe haḡaiḡa niduꞌa ḡurire haḡaiꞌuma.  
\v 10 Ebu aniꞌa sauꞌa haḡaiḡa nunu hina Badiꞌaꞌa ruiziteꞌe azaḡa soꞌoziꞌuma. Mazaḡa Badiꞌaꞌa ruiziteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa zeḡe ḡaboziteꞌe ḡoeꞌa huga zamare borofoga hezahoharo.  
\v 11 Eꞌe uꞌano, Badiꞌaꞌa zeḡe mazao soꞌosoꞌozeꞌeteꞌe inaraḡa tuḡunadu zeꞌa ḡuriro ḡoeꞌa mae ḡihiniꞌuma.  
\v 12 Zeꞌe ḡoere huga mene mae ḡihiniro, rehano haḡai veꞌoḡa haḡaeꞌenaꞌa matuꞌiro. Eꞌanoꞌo Badiꞌaꞌa zeḡe niduꞌa kotaziꞌuma.   
\s1 Badiꞌaꞌa Ḡabozifine Ohotiro  
\p
\v 13 Nego nabudi, zaꞌe Zuhiꞌa Boro zamarone azaḡa. Emeꞌe iḡaiḡa zae uꞌano Badiꞌa mazao manoḡa tauḡi rae huniꞌuma, mazaḡa zaꞌe Vine Zaḡoḡa hina zaḡozaḡifine zu ḡoere huga mae ḡihinadu ḡabone hidifine Badiꞌaꞌa ḡadaheḡano zae ohotiro.  
\v 14 Eꞌe veize, emeꞌa haramiroteꞌe hariḡa manoḡa hina Badiꞌaꞌa zae huziro. ꞌOugadu zae zuni emeḡe Zuhiꞌa Boro Iesu Keriso ni ḡihiꞌaḡa meiro.  
\v 15 Eꞌanoꞌo, nego nabudi, edau gigaranadu emeḡeꞌa hebe hina ziroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa ga soꞌa hina ihoziroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa obone giganoꞌi.   
\p
\v 16 Eme zae veize emeḡe Zuhiꞌa Boro Iesu Keriso zu Badiꞌa emeḡe Mama mazao kurauꞌohe. Badiꞌaꞌe emeḡe zamare borofeꞌohe. Aniꞌa emeḡe mazao manoḡa furenadu inarafiro onamo radiu tuḡutuḡu, ebu ḡabone tuḡutuḡu mae ḡihineꞌenaꞌa guhineꞌeteꞌe zamaroneḡa manoḡa rifiro.  
\v 17 Badiꞌa zu Iesuꞌa zamaze inaranoꞌi zu haḡaize manoḡa niduꞌa zu ḡoereze manoḡa niduꞌa zamaḡano inara ziniꞌenoꞌi.   
\c 3  
\s1 Kuranoga veize Umiziro  
\p
\v 1 Ḡonagano, nego nabudi, emeḡe veize kuranoꞌi. Aꞌe, Zuhiꞌa Boro hari manoḡaniꞌa zae boꞌaḡano bororaroteꞌe teige, vaze niduꞌa boꞌaḡano bororanadu zeꞌa mae ḡihinoga veize raꞌohe.  
\v 2 Ebu emeḡe sausaufeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa sauꞌa mazaonoꞌo Badiꞌaꞌa ḡabofoga veize kuranoꞌi, mazaḡa vaze boꞌaḡano mene niduꞌaꞌe Badiꞌa mazao fieꞌohe.  
\v 3 Rehano Zuhiꞌa Boroꞌe zamaḡa niduꞌa hina haḡaeꞌe ꞌahine, sauꞌa ḡauḡa, Satani mazaonoꞌo zae inaraziꞌuma zu biriꞌuma.  
\v 4 Zaꞌe Zuhiꞌa Boro mone azaḡa ꞌahine, emeꞌa haḡaoꞌi rae ziroteꞌe haḡaiḡa izidi haḡaeꞌeteꞌe ebu haḡae onamiteꞌe moneo emeꞌa hube hune edereꞌohe.  
\v 5 Zuhiꞌa Boroꞌa zamaze ibitohanadu Badiꞌaꞌa nougenouge zae zamare borofeꞌeteꞌe zaeꞌa ederifine emeꞌa kurauꞌohe, ebu Kerisoꞌa aduga zamaḡano zamaḡa obone giganiroteꞌe zaeꞌa ederadu zae zuni ꞌouge haḡaifine kurauꞌohe.   
\s1 Tubuḡa Azaḡa Riḡa Iraduguziro  
\p
\v 6 Nego nabudi, eme emeḡe Zuhiꞌa Boro Iesu Keriso niḡano riḡa ziꞌohe. Iniu tubuḡa zu emeḡeꞌa ihozidoteꞌe ihoreḡa idunaḡano mene radiuꞌeteꞌe negoḡa nabuga niduꞌa mazaonoꞌo vaḡinoꞌi.  
\v 7 Za zaeꞌa bare edeḡa, za nougenouge eme tuhutuhufiꞌuma. Emeḡeꞌa zae teite radiunuteꞌe madaḡano emeꞌe mene tubuḡa reiro.  
\v 8 Eme vaze ogomuꞌe naeḡa oꞌoꞌa mene mae au tauḡiro. Ebu zae boꞌaḡano vazeni ꞌahoga aduga mene hanoga veize, eme ohere zu madai, mada niduga gau boro inare haḡairo.  
\v 9 Emeꞌa ꞌouge haḡairotaꞌaꞌe mene mazaḡa zae mazaonoꞌo ogomu meiteꞌe inaraḡaꞌe oꞌoꞌa, rehano emeḡe haḡai zaeꞌa horonadu zae zuni emeḡe hegotifine raꞌohe.  
\v 10 Emeꞌa zae teite radiunuteꞌe madaḡano ꞌahige zido, “Iniuꞌa gauoga mene uratine, aniꞌe ogomu anoga zuni mene idaḡa.”   
\p
\v 11 Emeꞌa zae hari igiꞌetene, zae boꞌaḡano nuꞌe tubuḡa raꞌohe. Zeꞌe mene gaueꞌenaꞌa, vaze daꞌo dudizeꞌohe.  
\v 12 ꞌUguḡa azaḡaꞌe emeḡeꞌa Zuhiꞌa Boro Iesu Keriso niḡano ꞌahige riḡa ziꞌohe zu ihozeꞌohe, “Zaꞌe sifu gauoꞌi ebu zaeꞌa bare gauadu ogomu hidoꞌi.”  
\v 13 Nego nabudi, zaꞌe haḡai manoḡa haḡaeꞌeteꞌe zamaḡano ago fuḡozoꞌi.   
\p
\v 14 Iniu vazeꞌa emeḡeꞌa soꞌa ꞌada ihoziroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa mene hegotoꞌidene, vaze eꞌe faifaine ḡianoꞌi ebu ani teite ago zaꞌuoꞌi. ꞌOugine, ani aneꞌa bare mazagaroniꞌuma.  
\v 15 Rehano aniꞌe zae agire vazeḡa rae ago zamaroꞌi, rehano zae nego teige riḡa iradugunoꞌi.   
\s1 Ḡoere Ḡonaga  
\p
\v 16 Zama roḡeḡa rifiꞌeteꞌe Zuhiꞌaḡa Boroꞌa iḡaiḡa ibi niduꞌa zamaḡano ane zama roḡeḡa ziniꞌenoꞌi. Zuhiꞌa Boroꞌe zae niduꞌa teite radiuꞌenoꞌi.   
\p
\v 17 Uhiu ḡoeꞌa ꞌahiꞌe eḡe, Pauloꞌa eḡe ꞌevore hina miriheꞌohe. Aꞌe eḡe soꞌa niduꞌa zamaḡano eḡeꞌa mirihiro rae ihozeꞌeteꞌe tahiḡa, zu eḡeꞌa miriheꞌeteꞌe ibiḡa.   
\p
\v 18 Emeḡe Zuhiꞌa Boro Iesu Kerisoꞌa zae niduꞌa mazao manoḡa fureneꞌenoꞌi.   